query:
insert into underway.activity_call_attempt (
                activity_call_id,
                attempt_number,
                state,
                started_at,
                updated_at
            ) values (
                $1,
                1,
                'in_progress'::underway.activity_call_state,
                now() - interval '2 hours',
                now() - interval '2 hours'
            )
